casebody.data:
No. 09-8242. Thomas A. Vivone, Petitioner v. Thomas F. Simon, Clerk, Supreme Court of Missouri. 559 U.S. 968, 130 S. Ct. 1701,

176 L. Ed. 2d 177,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 1982. March 1, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Missouri dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
